cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper deals with the analysis of network traffic for the purpose of identifying the operating system, browser, and application of HTTPS traffic. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also uses machine learning algorithms for classification, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the resilience of the proposed solution to changes in network conditions, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CY).
